{"tid":2300243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭稱香港經濟萎縮應融入內地發展：今年得我哋國家有經濟增長","createTime":"2020-11-25T11:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T04:47:05.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9c3ca3f5d889a7bfd7ac4ad0728ea6fa1eab3f51","tid":2300243,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n「明日大嶼是非常值得的投資」<br />\n林鄭被問到香港未來經濟狀況，她坦言短期內難以反彈，但強調其經常性開支是歷屆政府之冠，又舉例自己在1997至2002亦曾處理財政困難，面對「肥雞餐」等，現時仍未去到當時的困境，不會縮減經常性開支；而改善經濟的唯一方法就是經濟增長，重申要融入中國經濟發展，稱「可能有經濟增長只係得我哋國家」。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/YFAZHVO43ZBGJGGZBWZ6HEJWBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FYFAZHVO43ZBGJGGZBWZ6HEJWBI%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=5a295831\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FYFAZHVO43ZBGJGGZBWZ6HEJWBI%2F&h=c584ef3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/YFAZHVO43ZBGJGGZBWZ6HEJWBI/</a>"},{"pid":"02ca23fdf14748fbc9f624a2264a663ab42be905","tid":2300243,"uid":135008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"威啦 支那周圍放毒害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba638f6a26e8f34a05c33765dd7dfd26a78de23","tid":2300243,"uid":74171,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"咩增長<br />\n負增長呀嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb0083d41c4e1d77d79d235b7b6ee208624aab8","tid":2300243,"uid":62318,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"有經濟增長咁威，咁要派錢還富於民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmo